snippet.title: Virtual Hunter | Gameplay Overview
snippet.description:
Virtual Hunter brings realistic hunting to virtual reality. In this video our lead designer explains the gameplay basics and shows what you can expect from the game!

You can wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1549850/Virtual_Hunter

Join our Discord server: https://discord.gg/gGmSAA8Prd
Follow us on Facebook: https://bit.ly/3DDP0QV
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/VirtualHunterVR
Website: http://virtualhuntervr.com

#virtualhuntervr #virtualreality #hunting
